Full-Stack E-Commerce Application (MERN Stack)
A fully functional e-commerce web application built using the MERN stack with real-world features like product management, cart, wishlist, orders, and payment integration.

ðŸ”¹ Features:

User authentication & authorization with JWT.

Product catalog with categories, subcategories, and variant-based options (size, color, price).

Advanced filters (brand, size, price range, specifications).

Cart & wishlist management linked to user accounts.

Address management for multiple delivery addresses.

Order placement system with Stripe and Razorpay payment gateways.

Admin panel for product management (add/edit products, manage variants, stock, and pricing).

Pagination & expandable filters for smooth browsing.

ðŸ›  Tech Stack:

Frontend: React, React Router, Context API (for state management), Tailwind CSS.

Backend: Node.js, Express.js.

Database: MongoDB (Mongoose).

Payments: Stripe, Razorpay.

Version Control & Deployment: Git/GitHub, Render/Netlify.

